// Template for personal VS Code overrides of the NovaVisor workspace.
// Copy to `novavisor.code-workspace` (git-ignored) and open with
// `File > Open Workspace from File...`.
//
// Syntax: JSONC (JSON with // comments) — VS Code parses it natively.
// Do not feed this file to strict JSON tools (e.g. `jq`) without stripping
// comments first.
//
// Precedence recap:
//   - `settings` here overrides .vscode/settings.json for this workspace only.
//   - `launch` / `tasks` are MERGED with the committed configs — your entries
//     appear alongside the shared ones in the Run/Task picker.
//
// All example entries below are commented out; uncomment what you want.
{
    "folders": [
        { "path": "." }
    ],
    "settings": {
